er experience and task completion rates, addressing another key pain point)\\n\\n**Option C (Dark Mode & Theme Customization):**\\n- Originality (1\u201310): 4 (Dark mode is a standard feature in most apps)\\n- Feasibility (1\u201310): 9 (Relatively easy to implement, mostly UI work)\\n- Impact (1\u201310): 7 (Addresses a user request and improves usability, especially in low-light conditions)\\n\\n### Final Picks & Why:\\n**Top Pick: Option A (Task Persistence & Sync Assurance)**\\n\\nWhile all three options address valid concerns, fixing the bug that causes tasks to disappear is paramount. Data loss is a major user experience killer and erodes trust in the app. Addressing this issue will have the biggest positive impact on user satisfaction.\\n\\n**Secondary Pick: Option B (Intelligent & Reliable Reminders)**\\n\\nAfter ensuring data is safe, improving the reliability of reminders is the next most important factor. Reminders are a core feature, and making them more dependable increases the value proposition of TaskBuddy. Option C, while desirable, is more of a cosmetic improvement and less critical than addressing functional issues.\\n',\n",
